<br>
At present we do ok at short term damage but the price in mana and aggro is too great most levels.  It really wouldn't take that much to get things to the right level - if Verant cares to do so. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urombusmindspire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rombus Mindspire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Forum Moderator</font></td></tr></table><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Verant's #1 Fanboy</font></td></tr></table></span><br>  Posts: 3823<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/25/02 9:42 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: short term</span><hr size=1> Actually you're right, we should be doing more damage in the short-term than any other class.  I take that part back.  We should be able to maintain damage output in the long-run though along the lines of Rog/Mnk-like damage... perhaps *slightly* less in the long-long-run. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/unicolheartsbane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nicol Heartsbane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br>  Posts: 543<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/25/02 1:08 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: short term</span><hr size=1> I would like spellshield a lot more if it didn't require a peridot.<br>
Runes and spellshields are not nearly as useful as a symbol anyway.<br>
<br>
Evac is incredibly useful.  It would be cool if it took your group mate's corpses to the zone line with you, of course, but that's a bit silly of me, and too hard for them to do anyway. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
The main advantage of a wizard is the ability to form groups of friends/guildies from all over the world, and rapidly assemble them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uizualxev.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Izual Xev</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/27/02 5:27 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: short term</span><hr size=1> melee proof mobs?!<br>
<br>
thats really silly.. when i post on the boards i try not to post as Izual the wizard i try to post as Izual the guildmate who wants to kill uber mobs and get phat loot..  makin melee proof mobs would suck... who would tank them?  hehe clerics and wizards back and forth as it got ponged around followed by the message  So_and_so_wizard was slain by New_Cool_Mob_Meant_to_Make_Wizards_l33t!<br>
