Rhag and Rumblecrush both have huge AC, 60 rogue using sapper/epic diddnt BS for more than 150 on rhag.  60 ranger with epic and primal landed a ton of 1 dmg hits on rumble.  i landed for full dmg on both these mobs with EVERY spell cast..<br>
